Jaylen Brown (30 points, nine rebounds) and Dennis Schroder (23 points, six rebounds, eight assists) added 53 points for the Celtics in the victory, while LaMelo Ball (25 points, five rebounds, nine assists) and Miles Bridges (25 points, ten rebounds) combined for 50 points for the Hornets in the losing effort. The Celtics improve to 2-2 on the season, while the Hornets fall to 3-1.

Led by Giannis Antetokounmpos 30 points, ten rebounds and nine assists, the Bucks defeated the Pacers, 119-109. Khris Middleton added 27 points, five rebounds and seven assists for the Bucks in the victory, while Malcolm Brogdon (25 points, seven assists) and Domantas Sabonis (21 points, 13 rebounds, five assists) combined for 46 points for the Pacers in the losing effort. The Bucks improve to 3-1 on the season, while the Pacers fall to 1-3.

The Hawks defeated the Pistons, 122-104. Trae Young led the Hawks with 32 points, four rebounds and nine assists, while John Collins added 22 points and seven rebounds in the victory. Saddiq Bey tallied 21 points and seven rebounds for the Pistons in the losing effort. The Hawks improve to 2-1 on the season, while the Pistons fall to 0-3.

Led by Jimmy Butlers 36 points (15-21 FG) and five steals, the Heat defeated the Magic, 107-90. Bam Adebayo (16 points, 13 rebounds) and Tyler Herro (13 points, five rebounds, nine assists) added a combined 29 points for the Heat in the victory, while Cole Anthony tallied 12 points, nine rebounds and five assists for the Magic in the losing effort. The Heat improve to 2-1 on the season, while the Magic fall to 1-3.

The Bulls defeated the Raptors, 111-108. DeMar DeRozan led the Bulls with 26 points and six assists, while Zach LaVine tallied 22 points and five assists in the victory. Fred VanVleet tallied 15 points, six rebounds and a career-high 17 assists for the Raptors in the losing effort. The Bulls improve to 4-0 on the season, while the Raptors fall to 1-3.

The Nets defeated the Wizards, 104-90. Kevin Durant led the Nets with 25 points and eight rebounds, while James Harden added 14 points, six rebounds and nine assists in the victory. Bradley Beal tallied 19 points and four assists for the Wizards in the losing effort. The Nets improve to 2-2 on the season, while the Wizards fall to 2-1.

Led by Jonas Valanciunas 22 points and 23 rebounds, the Pelicans defeated the Timberwolves, 107-98. Brandon Ingram added 27 points and nine rebounds for the Pelicans in the victory, while Karl-Anthony Towns (32 points, 14 rebounds, seven assists) and Anthony Edwards (28 points, nine rebounds) combined for 60 points for the Timberwolves in the losing effort. The Pelicans improve to 1-3 on the season, while the Timberwolves fall to 2-1.
Items.vs: Minnesota Timberwolves vs. New Orleans Pelicans

Items.description: The Cavaliers defeated the Nuggets, 99-87. Jarrett Allen led the Cavaliers with 21 points (10-11 FG) and 16 rebounds, while Kevin Love added a team-high 22 points, along with six rebounds in the victory. Nikola Jokic tallied 24 points, 19 rebounds and three steals for the Nuggets in the losing effort. The Cavaliers improve to 2-2 on the season, while the Nuggets fall to 2-1.

Led by Paul Georges 16 points and career-high eight steals, the Clippers defeated the Trail Blazers, 116-86. Luke Kennard added 23 points (6-7 3pt FG) for the Clippers in the victory, while CJ McCollum (20 points, four assists) and Damian Lillard (12 points, 0-8 3pt FG) combined for 32 points for the Trail Blazers in the losing effort. The Clippers improve to 1-2 on the season, while the Trail Blazers fall to 1-2.
Items.vs: LA Clippers vs. Portland Trail Blazers

Items.description: The Knicks defeated the 76ers, 112-99. Kemba Walker tallied a team-high 19 points, along with five assists for the Knicks, while Julius Randle added 16 points, 11 rebounds and seven assists in the victory. Tobias Harris tallied 23 points, nine rebounds and nine assists for the 76ers, while Joel Embiid added 14 points, six rebounds and three assists in the losing effort. The Knicks improve to 3-1 on the season, while the 76ers fall to 2-2.

The Warriors defeated the Thunder, 106-98. Stephen Curry recorded a team-high 23 points, along with six rebounds and four assists for the Warriors, while Andrew Wiggins added 21 points in the victory. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander led all scorers with 30 points and four assists for the Thunder in the losing effort. The Warriors improve to 4-0 on the season, while the Thunder fall to 0-4.
Items.vs: Oklahoma City Thunder vs. Golden State Warriors

Items.description: The Mavericks defeated the Rockets, 116-106. Luka Doncic led the way for the Mavericks with 26 points, 14 rebounds and seven assists, while Jalen Green tallied 10 points and five rebounds for the Rockets in the losing effort. The Mavericks improve to 2-1 on the season, while the Rockets fall to 1-3.

The Lakers defeated the Spurs in overtime, 125-121. Anthony Davis (35 points, 17 rebounds, four blocks) and Russell Westbrook (33 points, ten rebounds, eight assists) combined for 68 points for the Lakers, while Dejounte Murray tallied 21 points, 12 rebounds and a career-high 15 assists for the Spurs in the losing effort, his 5th career triple-double. The Lakers improve to 2-2 on the season, while the Spurs fall to 1-3.
Items.vs: San Antonio Spurs vs. Los Angeles Lakers

Items.description: The Jazz defeated the Nuggets, 122-110. Rudy Gobert recorded a team-high 23 points (7-8 FG) and 16 rebounds for the Jazz, while Donovan Mitchell added 22 points and six assists in the victory. Will Barton tallied 21 points, four rebounds and three assists for the Nuggets in the losing effort. The Jazz improve to 3-0 on the season, while the Nuggets fall to 2-2.

Led by Miles Bridges 31 points and six rebounds, the Hornets defeated the Magic, 120-111. Gordon Hayward (24 points, five rebounds, five assists) and LaMelo Ball (seven points, six rebounds, three assists) added 31 points for the Hornets, while Cole Anthony tallied a team-high 24 points, along with five rebounds and six assists for the Magic in the losing effort. The Hornets improve to 4-1 on the season, while the Magic fall to 1-4.

The Raptors defeated the Pacers, 118-100. Fred VanVleet led the way for the Raptors with 26 points and six assists, along with a career-high ten rebounds, while Scottie Barnes added 18 points, seven rebounds and seven assists in the victory. Chris Duarte tallied 14 points and four rebounds for the Pacers in the losing effort. The Raptors improve to 2-3 on the season, while the Pacers fall to 1-4.

The Wizards defeated the Celtics, 116-107. Montrezl Harrell led all scorers with 25 points and 11 rebounds for the Wizards, while Bradley Beal added 17 points and ten rebounds in the victory. Jayson Tatum tallied 23 points and seven rebounds for the Celtics in the losing effort. The Wizards improve to 3-1 on the season, while the Celtics fall to 2-3.

After trailing by as many as 16 points, the Hawks defeated the Pelicans, 102-99. Trae Young led the way for the Hawks with 31 points, five rebounds and seven assists, while John Collins added 16 points and 12 rebounds in the victory. Brandon Ingram tallied 20 points, eight rebounds and four assists for the Pelicans in the losing effort. The Hawks improve to 3-1 on the season, while the Pelicans fall to 1-4
Items.vs: New Orleans Pelicans vs. Atlanta Hawks

Items.description: The Heat defeated the Nets, 106-93. Jimmy Butler recorded 17 points, 14  rebounds, seven assists and four steals for the Heat, while Bam Adebayo added a team-high 24 points, along with nine rebounds in the victory. Kevin Durant led all scorers with 25 points and 11 rebounds for the Nets in the losing effort. The Heat improve to 3-1 on the season, while the Nets fall to 2-3.

After trailing by as many as 26 points, the Thunder defeated the Lakers, 123-115. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander recorded 27 points, nine rebounds and five assists for the Thunder, while Josh Giddey, the No. 6 overall pick in the 2021 NBA Draft from Australia, added 18 points and ten assists in the victory. Russell Westbrook tallied 20 points, 14 rebounds, 13 assists and ten turnovers for the Lakers in the losing effort, his 1st triple-double of the season and the 185th of his career. The Thunder improve to 1-4 on the season, while the Lakers fall to 2-3.
Items.vs: Oklahoma City Thunder vs. Los Angeles Lakers

Items.description: Despite Giannis Antetokounmpos 40 points, 16 rebounds, seven assists and three blocks, the Timberwolves defeated the Bucks, 113-108. DAngelo Russell recorded a team-high 29 points, along with five rebounds and six assists for the Timberwolves, while Anthony Edwards (25 points, seven rebounds, three assists) and Karl-Anthony Towns (25 points, five assists) added a combined 50 points in the victory. The Timberwolves improve to 3-1 on the season, while the Bucks fall to 3-2.

Harrison Barnes knocked down a three-pointer from the left wing as time expired in regulation to lift the Kings over the Suns, 110-107. Barnes finished with 22 points, nine rebounds and four assists for the Kings, while DeAaron Fox added 18 points and nine assists in the victory. Devin Booker (31 points, six rebounds, eight assists) and Deandre Ayton (21 points, 21 rebounds) combined for 52 points for the Suns in the losing effort. The Kings improve to 2-2 on the season, while the Suns fall to 1-3.

The Trail Blazers defeated the Grizzlies, 116-96. CJ McCollum led all scorers with 25 points for the Trail Blazers, while Damian Lillard added 20 points and ten assists in the victory. Ja Morant tallied 17 points, nine rebounds and ten assists for the Grizzlies in the losing effort. The Trail Blazers improve to 2-2 on the season, while the Grizzlies fall to 2-2.

Items.description: The Cavaliers defeated the Clippers, 92-79. Collin Sexton led all scorers with 26 points and seven rebounds for the Cavaliers, while Darius Garland added 16 points, four rebounds and six assists in the victory. Paul George tallied 12 points, ten rebounds and four steals for the Clippers in the losing effort. The Cavaliers improve to 3-2 on the season, while the Clippers fall to 1-3.
